name: Harvest Netflix Enhanced High Income Shares ETF
longDescription: In order to achieve its investment objectives, Harvest Netflix Enhanced High Income Shares ETF will invest up to 100% of its total assets in the common stock class A of Netflix and will write covered call options on shares of Netflix. The proportion of covered call options written will vary depending on market conditions and will be based on the Harvest ETFs distribution policy, subject to a maximum 50% write level. Harvest Netflix Enhanced High Income Shares ETF will seek to provide Unitholders with (i) longterm capital appreciation by investing, directly or indirectly, on a levered basis, in the common stock of Netflix, Inc. (Netflix) and (ii) high monthly cash distributions.
